{"data":[{"date":"04:02 27/06","title":"Ph\u00e1p th\u00e0 nh\u1ea1t nh\u1ebdo c\u00f2n h\u01a1n h\u00fat ch\u1ebft nh\u01b0 \u0110\u1ee9c hay TBN","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/phap-tha-nhat-nheo-con-hon-hut-chet-nhu-duc-hay-tbn.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Didier Deschamps l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng thanh minh cho m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a thi\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1i \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 0-0 Ph\u00e1p h\u1ea1 m\u00e0n b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ph\u00e1p gi\u00e0nh quy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f3 ai c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u00e0 thuy\u1ebft ph\u1ee5c, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t so v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng l\u1edbn lao \u0111\u1eb7t v\u00e0o d\u00e0n sao \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Didier Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 0-0 Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Didier Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 0-0 Ph\u00e1p h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/phap-tha-nhat-nheo-con-hon-hut-chet-nhu-duc-hay-tbn.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 0-0 Ph\u00e1p</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Hai chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt tr\u01b0\u1edbc Australia v\u00e0 Peru gi\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ti\u1ebfp n\u1ed1i b\u1edfi tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a nh\u1ea1t nh\u1ebdo 0-0 v\u1edbi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, khi\u1ebfn World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi kh\u00f4ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. D\u1eaft tay nhau \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch, la \u00f3 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1edbt t\u1eeb tr\u00ean c\u00e1c kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">HLV Didier Deschamps ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-dan-mach-vs-phap-463-189638.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 0-0 Ph\u00e1p</span> l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng thanh minh cho th\u00eam m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ngh\u00e8o n\u00e0n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2, \u00f4ng n\u00f3i: \u201cQuan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh v\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi t\u01b0 t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u h\u00f2a n\u00ean m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng g\u00ec cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n th\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u201cN\u00f3 ph\u1ee9c t\u1ea1p h\u01a1n c\u00e1c anh ngh\u0129 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea5y. H\u00e3y nh\u00ecn \u0110\u1ee9c hay T\u00e2y Ban Nha ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng xem v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i h\u1ecd c\u0169ng h\u00fat ch\u1ebft trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 mu\u1ed1n Ph\u00e1p nh\u01b0 v\u1eady, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n c\u0169ng hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf tr\u1eadn c\u1edfi m\u1edf h\u01a1n \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n knock-out. H\u00f4m nay m\u1ecdi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 v\u00e0 khi\u1ebfn t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng.\u201d<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ngay tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean m\u1edf m\u00e0n v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 (21h00 ng\u00e0y th\u1ee9 b\u1ea3y 30/6) s\u1ebd ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn si\u00eau \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p vs Argentina. Lionel Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edbi l\u00e1ch qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p b\u1eb1ng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-dan-mach-vs-phap-461-189661.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 0-0 Ph\u00e1p (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-dan-mach-vs-phap-421-189643.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-dan-mach-vs-phap.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-dan-mach-vs-phap-421-189643.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018</span><br>\r\nChuy\u00ean trang Bongda24h c\u1eadp nh\u1eadt chi ti\u1ebft k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018 h\u00f4m nay. Th\u00f4ng tin k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n, clip b\u00e0n...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"618","checkdouble":"189681"},{"date":"04:06 27/06","title":"HLV \u0110an M\u1ea1ch l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a 0-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/5/26/doi-thu-tai-world-cup-2018-xem-thuong-tuyen-phap.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u01b0\u1edbc vi\u1ec7c b\u1ecb t\u1ed1 thi \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u1ea1t nh\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng cho r\u1eb1ng c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018, \u0110T \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 4 \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f2n Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau hai tr\u1eadn to\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec th\u1ebf, n\u1ebfu tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 h\u00f2a th\u00ec hai \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c d\u1eaft tay nhau \u0111i ti\u1ebfp m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. V\u00e0 di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra theo \u0111\u00fang k\u1ecbch b\u1ea3n m\u00e0 ph\u00eda \u0110an M\u1ea1ch ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huan luyen vien Age Hareide danh gia thap doi tuyen Phap o World Cup 2018.\" title=\"Hu\u1ea5n luy\u1ec7n vi\u00ean Age Hareide \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Ph\u00e1p \u1edf World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/26/doi-thu-tai-world-cup-2018-xem-thuong-tuyen-phap.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV \u0110an M\u1ea1ch&nbsp;Age Hareide b\u00e1c b\u1ecf chuy\u1ec7n ch\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ee7 h\u00f2a \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Su\u1ed1t 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u, hai \u0111\u1ed9i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u1ec1 ph\u00eda khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a nhau. C\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Ph\u00e1p kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong khi \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u1eeba \u0111\u00e1 v\u1eeba nghe ng\u00f3ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i gi\u1eefa Peru v\u00e0 \u00dac.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110an M\u1ea1ch vs Ph\u00e1p c\u0169ng k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 h\u00f2a 0-0 \u0111\u01b0a c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ed9i l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng trong. Tuy nhi\u00ean sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V hai \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean khi\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ebb nh\u1ea1t v\u00e0 k\u00e9m ph\u1ea7n s\u00f4i \u0111\u1ed9ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn, HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T \u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u00f4ng Age Hareide cho hay: &ldquo;Nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi ngh\u0129 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng th\u1ee7 h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf, \u0110an M\u1ea1ch h\u00f4m nay \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi. S\u1ebd l\u00e0 ngu ng\u1ed1c n\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f4ng v\u1edbi h\u1ecd. \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u1ea7n k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng qu\u00ean kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 r\u01a1i v\u00e0o b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng g\u00ec c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ec1u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng. &ldquo;\u0110an M\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m \u1edf m\u1ed9t b\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh t\u1eebng \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i cu\u1ed1i c\u0169ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi l\u00e0 Croatia, HLV Hareide n\u00f3i th\u00eam: &ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t m\u1ea1nh. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 xem c\u00e1ch h\u1ecd thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng r\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1ng g\u1eddm&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa \u0110an M\u1ea1ch v\u00e0 Croatia s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 1/7 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u1eb7p n\u00e0y s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u1edf c\u1eb7p T\u00e2y Ban Nha/Nga \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ebd l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ea1i Sochi v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 7/7.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-dan-mach-vs-phap-461-189661.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-dan-mach-vs-phap.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-dan-mach-vs-phap-461-189661.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: \u0110an M\u1ea1ch 0-0 Ph\u00e1p (B\u1ea3ng C World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang nh\u01b0 lo ng\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia, hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u00f2a nh\u00e3, nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n \u0111\u1ebfn bu\u1ed3n ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 ra....</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-dan-mach-vs-phap-463-189638.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-dan-mach-vs-phap.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-dan-mach-vs-phap-463-189638.html\">\u0110an M\u1ea1ch 0-0 Ph\u00e1p (KT): Les Bleus dung d\u0103ng dung d\u1ebb d\u1eaft l\u00ednh ch\u00ec v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8</span><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang nh\u01b0 lo ng\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a nhi\u1ec1u chuy\u00ean gia, hai \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 h\u00f2a nh\u00e3, nh\u00e0m ch\u00e1n \u0111\u1ebfn bu\u1ed3n ng\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ea1t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u0111\u1ec1 ra....</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/christian-eriksen-dan-mach-co-the-dong-vai-phan-dien-khong-phai-anh-421-189245.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/22/christian-eriksen-dan-mach-co-the-dong-vai-phan-dien-khong-phai-anh.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/christian-eriksen-dan-mach-co-the-dong-vai-phan-dien-khong-phai-anh-421-189245.html\">Christian Eriksen: \u0110an M\u1ea1ch c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00f3ng vai ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n, kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i anh!</span><br>\r\nLi\u1ec7t k\u00ea th\u1eed xem nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ee7a k\u1ef3 World Cup n\u0103m nay n\u00e0o! Argentina c\u1ee7a Lionel Messi, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a Cristiano Ronaldo, Ai C\u1eadp c\u1ee7a Mohamed Salah,...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"617","checkdouble":"189682"},{"date":"03:49 27/06","title":"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/thong-ke-gay-soc-tran-nigeria-12-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria t\u1ed1i 26/6, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Messi cho bi\u1ebft anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c Argentina s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D \u1edf VCK World Cup 2018, \u0110T Argentina \u0111ang t\u1ea1m x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nigeria.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"messi argentina\" title=\"messi argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/messi-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-nghet-tho-truoc-nigeria.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Messi ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap Argentina c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi d\u00f9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0y, M10 \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb TyC Sports: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng Argentina s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Ch\u00faa tr\u1eddi lu\u00f4n b\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 Ng\u00e0i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c Argentina. T\u00f4i xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0110T Argentina v\u00ec s\u1ef1 hy sinh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng C\u0110V lu\u00f4n d\u00f5i theo v\u00e0 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Rojo&nbsp;&ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 l\u1ea1i chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;B\u00e2y gi\u1edd th\u00ec World Cup m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Messi \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y t\u00f4i xin d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i v\u00e0 cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u1ed1 l\u00ean Argentina!&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Argentina s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Ph\u00e1p \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i Th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y 30/6 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i th\u1eafng trong c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u1edf g\u1eb7p Uruguay/B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-argentina-vs-nigeria-461-189678.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/Ket-qua-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-tran-dau-bang-D-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-argentina-vs-nigeria-461-189678.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nigeria 1-2 Argentina (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nMessi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p sau 90 ph\u00fat ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf. Messi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0ng Moses g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. Cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Argentina may m\u1eafn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-argentina-vs-nigeria-463-189665.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-argentina-vs-nigeria.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-argentina-vs-nigeria-463-189665.html\">Nigeria 1-2 Argentina (KT): C\u1ee9u tinh Rojo \u0111\u01b0a Albiceleste v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u1ef1c ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c</span><br>\r\nMessi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p sau 90 ph\u00fat ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf. Messi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0ng Moses g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. Cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Argentina may m\u1eafn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"616","checkdouble":"189683"},{"date":"04:14 27/06","title":"B\u1ecb Argentina lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng HLV Nigeria n\u00f3i g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/bi-argentina-loai-day-cay-dang-hlv-nigeria-noi-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 64 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nigeria b\u1ecb Argentina lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc khi l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 di\u1ec5n ra, duy nh\u1ea5t Croatia l\u00e0 c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp 3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i s\u1ebd c\u1ea1nh tranh m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc v\u00e9 c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nigeria \u0111ang x\u1ebfp th\u1ee9 2 v\u1edbi 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m, h\u1ecd t\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean c\u00f3 l\u1ee3i th\u1ebf c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i so v\u1edbi Argentina v\u00e0 Iceland, nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/HLV-Gernot-Rohr-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Nigeria thua Argentina 1-2</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n gi\u00e0nh 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina, Nigeria s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c \u0111i ti\u1ebfp m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n quan t\u00e2m \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i. Th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 c\u00fang gi\u00fap h\u1ecd r\u1ed9ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u00fang v\u1edbi t\u00ednh ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft b\u1ea3ng D, Argentina v\u00e0 Nigeria \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m. Messi gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t l\u00ean, song s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a \u201c\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh\u201d gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a \u1edf ph\u00fat 51.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp Argentina bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i th\u1eafng, b\u1edfi v\u1eady h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed5ng l\u1ef1c. Nigeria \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t tho\u00e1ng m\u1ea5t t\u1eadp trung khi\u1ebfn h\u1ecd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 gi\u00e1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nPh\u00fat 86, Marcos Rojo d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-argentina-vs-nigeria-421-189676.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Nigeria vs Argentina</span> c\u1ed9ng v\u1edbi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 1-2 c\u1ee7a Iceland tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia gi\u00fap Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f9ng Croatia b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCroatia \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u c\u00f2n Argentina x\u1ebfp \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ee9 2. Nigeria v\u00e0 Iceland l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed3i \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Gernot Rohr \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 64 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u1edf c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gernot Rohr phat bieu ve tran Nigeria vs Argentina\" title=\"Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/bi-argentina-loai-day-cay-dang-hlv-nigeria-noi-gi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gernot Rohr ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cNigeria \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb v\u00e0 nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m, song ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n th\u1ef1c h\u00f3a \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c4 n\u0103m sau l\u1ee9a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 m\u00e0 Nigeria \u0111ang c\u00f3 s\u1ebd tr\u01b0\u1edfng th\u00e0nh h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n c\u1ea3m \u01a1n nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng trong su\u1ed1t th\u1eddi gian qua. C\u00f2n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd, t\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"615","checkdouble":"189684"},{"date":"04:34 27/06","title":"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng tr\u1eadn Iceland 1-2 Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/thong-ke-an-tuong-tran-iceland-12-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Iceland \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi \u0111\u1ec3 thua Croatia v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2, c\u00f9ng nh\u00ecn l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Iceland vs Croatia \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>3 - </strong>Ivan Perisic \u0111\u00e3 ghi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng cho Croatia \u1edf World Cup, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Davor Suker (6) ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Inter Milan.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Iceland vs Croatia - B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Iceland vs Croatia - B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Thong-ke-Iceland-vs-Croatia---Bang-D-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Perisic c\u00f3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 3 cho Croatia \u1edf World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>17 \u2013</strong> \u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn 17 qu\u1ea3 11m, b\u1eb1ng v\u1edbi k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n th\u1ed5i ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n \u1edf World Cup 1998.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>2 \u2013</strong> Croatia ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch c\u00f3 2 l\u1ea7n \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Iceland v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-croatia-vs-iceland-421-189675.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Iceland vs Croatia</span> gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc ca r\u00f4 k\u1ebft th\u00fac v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>3 \u2013</strong> Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Iceland vs Croatia ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1ecdc ca r\u00f4 \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eafng c\u1ea3 3 tr\u1eadn \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>100% -</strong> 80 ph\u00fat tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Mateo Kovacic th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n 79 \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c 100%.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>2 - </strong>Sigurdsson tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 hai \u0111\u00e3 1 l\u1ea7n ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0 1 l\u1ea7n s\u00fat h\u1ecfng tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m \u1edf World Cup 2018, sau Cristiano Ronaldo c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Iceland vs Croatia - B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Iceland vs Croatia - B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Thong-ke-Iceland-vs-Croatia---Bang-D-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh-2.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sigurdsson g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1 cho Iceland tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h3>\u00a0</h3>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>2 \u2013</strong> \u0110\u00e2y m\u1edbi l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a Milan Badelj cho \u0110T Croatia, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean anh ghi v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Malta \u1edf v\u00f2ng lo\u1ea1i Euro 2012 v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 9 n\u0103m 2011.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>10 \u2013</strong> 10/11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia \u1edf World Cup \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi trong hi\u1ec7p 2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"614","checkdouble":"189685"},{"date":"04:35 27/06","title":"Messi n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/messi-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-nghet-tho-truoc-nigeria.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria t\u1ed1i 26/6, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Messi cho bi\u1ebft anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c Argentina s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00e3 x\u1ea3y ra.</h2><br>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D \u1edf VCK World Cup 2018, \u0110T Argentina \u0111ang t\u1ea1m x\u1ebfp cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng v\u1edbi v\u1ecfn v\u1eb9n 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m. Tuy nhi\u00ean h\u1ecd v\u1eabn c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp n\u1ebfu \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nigeria.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"messi argentina\" title=\"messi argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/messi-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-nghet-tho-truoc-nigeria.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Messi ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap Argentina c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng knock-out World Cup 2018</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u00e0 \u0111\u00fang nh\u01b0 nh\u1eefng d\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e1n, Messi v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi d\u00f9 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 nh\u1ecdc nh\u1eb1n. N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i quan tr\u1ecdng n\u00e0y, M10 \u0111\u00e3 chia s\u1ebb TyC Sports: &ldquo;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng r\u1eb1ng Argentina s\u1ebd gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft Ch\u00faa tr\u1eddi lu\u00f4n b\u00ean m\u00ecnh v\u00e0 Ng\u00e0i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecf m\u1eb7c Argentina. T\u00f4i xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n t\u1edbi t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean \u0110T Argentina v\u00ec s\u1ef1 hy sinh c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd, v\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng C\u0110V lu\u00f4n d\u00f5i theo v\u00e0 \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Rojo&nbsp;&ndash; ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u00fap Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 l\u1ea1i chia s\u1ebb: &ldquo;B\u00e2y gi\u1edd th\u00ec World Cup m\u1edbi th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u. Messi \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i anh \u1ea5y s\u1ebd l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. B\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0y t\u00f4i xin d\u00e0nh t\u1eb7ng cho gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i v\u00e0 cho to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. C\u1ed1 l\u00ean Argentina!&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Argentina s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u Ph\u00e1p \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o t\u1ed1i Th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y 30/6 t\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ed9i th\u1eafng trong c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1ea1i World Cup n\u0103m nay g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i th\u1eafng \u1edf g\u1eb7p Uruguay/B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-argentina-vs-nigeria-461-189678.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/Ket-qua-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-tran-dau-bang-D-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-argentina-vs-nigeria-461-189678.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nigeria 1-2 Argentina (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nMessi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p sau 90 ph\u00fat ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf. Messi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0ng Moses g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. Cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Argentina may m\u1eafn...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-argentina-vs-nigeria-463-189665.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-argentina-vs-nigeria.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-argentina-vs-nigeria-463-189665.html\">Nigeria 1-2 Argentina (KT): C\u1ee9u tinh Rojo \u0111\u01b0a Albiceleste v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u1ef1c ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c</span><br>\r\nMessi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p sau 90 ph\u00fat ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf. Messi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0ng Moses g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. Cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Argentina may m\u1eafn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"613","checkdouble":"189686"},{"date":"05:04 27/06","title":"\"C\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Leicester c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf World Cup 2018\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/cau-chuyen-co-tich-cua-leicester-co-the-xuat-hien-o-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Phil Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018, c\u1ef1u sao MU v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n Anh tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Leicester \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phil Neville th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u00ec c\u00e1c \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nWorld Cup 2018 \u0111ang \u0111i \u0111\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, h\u01a1n m\u1ed9t n\u1eeda s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn c\u1ee7a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n. \u0110i\u1ec3n h\u00ecnh nh\u01b0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110\u1ee9c, Argentina hay vi\u1ec7c Ba Lan b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i ch\u1ec9 sau 2 l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phil Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Phil Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Phil-Neville-phat-bieu-ve-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Argentina ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00e0 MU, Phil Neville kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh anh kh\u00f4ng \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cPh\u00e1p, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u0110\u1ee9c, Argentina hay Brazil l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u1ee9ng vi\u00ean l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t cho danh hi\u1ec7u v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch, nh\u01b0ng nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 h\u1ecd th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng v\u1edbi t\u00f4i. D\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u1ee9c l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i \u0110KV\u0110 nh\u01b0ng thua Mexico \u1edf ng\u00e0y ra qu\u00e2n, \u00e1 qu\u00e2n Argentina ch\u1ec9 gi\u00e0nh 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m sau 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. Ph\u00e1p, Brazil, TBN hay B\u0110N \u0111\u1ec1u g\u1eb7p r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i k\u1ef3 World Cup c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Phil Neville tin \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng nh\u1ecf c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00ean ng\u00f4i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Phil Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 World Cup 2018, c\u1ef1u sao MU v\u00e0 tuy\u1ec3n Anh tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u00edch c\u1ee7a Leicester \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u00e1i hi\u1ec7n \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Phil Neville ung ho Van Gaal\" title=\"Phil Neville \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Van Gaal\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2015/12/23/cuu-sao-mu-het-muc-ung-ho-van-gaal.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Phil Neville tin r\u1eb1ng c\u00e2u chuy\u1ec7n c\u1ed5 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Leicester c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cKhi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00f4ng ch\u01a1i \u0111\u00fang \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ebfn v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0110an M\u1ea1ch, Croatia hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed l\u00e0 Mexico\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cLeicester \u0111\u00e3 t\u1eebng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Premier League, n\u00ean nh\u1edb r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra trong 38 v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u. B\u1edfi v\u1eady \u1edf m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra ch\u1ec9 trong v\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t th\u00e1ng nh\u1eefng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1ea3y ra. T\u00f4i linh c\u1ea3m s\u1ebd c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u00fa s\u1ed1c \u1edf World Cup 2018\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a Phil Neville kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 s\u1edf khi m\u00e0 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-argentina-vs-nigeria-463-189665.html\" target=\"_blank\">Argentina ch\u1eadt v\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp</span>, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 \u0110\u1ee9c hay Brazil v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc ngay t\u01b0 v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"612","checkdouble":"189688"},{"date":"05:23 27/06","title":"\u0110\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Nigeria: \"Argentina \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u1edd tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/doi-truong-nigeria-argentina-di-tiep-nho-trong-tai.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Jon Obi Mikel n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigria vs Argentina, c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nigeria th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7y cay \u0111\u1eafng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNigeria ch\u1ec9 c\u1ea7n h\u00f2a Argentina \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i b\u1ea3ng D l\u00e0 s\u1ebd s\u00e1ng c\u1eeda \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, b\u1edfi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd Iceland kh\u00f4ng d\u1ec5 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Croatia.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t cao, &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh&rdquo; \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcos Rojo lai ghi ban vao luoi Nigeria\" title=\"Marcos Rojo l\u1ea1i ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Nigeria\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/rojo.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marcos Rojo gi\u00fap Argentina \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 Messi c\u00f3 ghi b\u00e0n m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 t\u1eeb kh\u00e1 s\u1edbm th\u00ec Nigeria v\u1eabn ki\u00ean tr\u00ec v\u1edbi l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt h\u1ee3p l\u00fd c\u00f9ng quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m r\u1ea5t cao gi\u00fap h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 \u1edf ph\u00fat 51. Sau \u0111\u00f3, Argentina t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ee9c \u00e9p r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn nh\u01b0ng h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Nigeria v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ee9ng v\u1eefng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKhi m\u00e0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Nigeria phong t\u1ecfa th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng Messi hay Higuain th\u00ec h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ed9t h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 ch\u1ecdc kh\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi. Ph\u00fat 86, Marcos Rojo l\u00ean tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ph\u00fat c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i, Nigelia \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ed3n to\u00e0n l\u1ef1c t\u00ecm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-argentina-vs-nigeria-421-189676.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Nigeria vs Argentina</span> khi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2u Phi ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Jon Obi Mikel ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Jon Obi Mikel n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigria vs Argentina, c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Jon Obi Mikel phat bieu ve tran Nigeria vs Argentina\" title=\"Jon Obi Mikel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/doi-truong-nigeria-argentina-di-tiep-nho-trong-tai.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Jon Obi Mikel ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 11m cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay Rojo trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u01b0\u1edfng 11, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y xem l\u1ea1i video v\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o VAR. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y n\u00f3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m tay, t\u00f4i h\u1ecfi t\u1ea1i sao kh\u00f4ng cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng 11m, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i 1 qu\u1ea3 11m h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nigeria \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t trong ng\u00e0y h\u00f4m nay, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 thua v\u00ec quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"611","checkdouble":"189689"},{"date":"06:38 27/06","title":"Messi \u0111\u01b0a Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1eeda t\u1eed: Lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng ch\u00f3i h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3!","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/e.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Marcos Rojo s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng v\u1edbi pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh trong chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng Nigeria 1-2 Argentina k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u00e0 ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n anh c\u0169ng s\u1ebd vui v\u1ebb ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t bi\u1ebfn r\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi ti\u00eau \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i Lionel Messi.</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u00c1p l\u1ef1c t\u00e2m l\u00fd c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u bu\u1ed3n c\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed1i v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t con ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi tr\u1edf n\u00ean y\u1ebfu \u0111u\u1ed1i, ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f3c l\u00f3c nh\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00ec \u0111\u1ee9ng d\u1eady m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd. V\u00e0 r\u1ed3i c\u00f3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1eaft volley qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ec3 ch\u01b0a t\u1eebng l\u00e0m \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 trong \u0111\u1eddi. Marcos Rojo &ndash; \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac, \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ed7 v\u00e0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u00fang ng\u01b0\u1eddi.</p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi \u1edf tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina Lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Messi \u1edf tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina Lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Messi-o-tran-Nigeria-1-2-Argentina-Luon-la-ngoi-sao-sang-nhat!-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marcos Rojo s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng nh\u01b0ng Leo Messi \u1edf tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t!</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ef1c t\u1ebf \u0111\u00e2y c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1eddi khen &ldquo;\u0111\u1ec3u&rdquo; d\u00e0nh cho Argentina khi cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng, m\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eabn ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 trong kh\u1ed5 s\u1edf, h\u1ecd c\u0169ng cho ra m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 &ldquo;ra t\u1ea5m ra m\u00f3n&rdquo; \u1edf World Cup l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, \u00edt nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi c\u00f4ng c\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ee7 ch\u1eafc v\u00e0 gi\u00e0u s\u1ee9c chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria h\u01a1n h\u1eb3n <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/argentina-va-con-ac-mong-nuoc-nga-messi-oan-minh-ganh-team-oan-minh-chiu-toi-den-bao-gio-421-189352.html\" target=\"_blank\">hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga</span>.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u01a1 m\u00e0 ai m\u00e0 \u0111i quan t\u00e2m cho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 ch\u1ee9? K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 t\u1ed3n t\u1ea1i duy nh\u1ea5t, nh\u1eefng th\u1ee9 kh\u00e1c c\u00f3 ra sao kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m sinh t\u1eed Argentina vs Nigeria, Jorge Sampaoli n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 n\u0103m tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft tr\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ebfn Moscow n\u00e2ng cao c\u00fap v\u00e0ng. M\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e3 xong, c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i b\u1ed1n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/argentina-va-con-ac-mong-nuoc-nga-messi-oan-minh-ganh-team-oan-minh-chiu-toi-den-bao-gio-421-189352.html\">Argentina v\u00e0 c\u01a1n \u00e1c m\u1ed9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga: Messi o\u1eb1n m\u00ecnh g\u00e1nh team, o\u1eb1n m\u00ecnh ch\u1ecbu t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ebfn bao gi\u1edd?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong v\u00f2ng n\u0103m ng\u00e0y k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau \u0111\u1ea1i b\u1ea1i ba b\u00e0n tr\u1eafng d\u01b0\u1edbi tay Croatia, n\u1ed9i b\u1ed9 Argentina n\u1ea3y sinh h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n ti\u00eau c\u1ef1c r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00ednh ch\u00ednh tr\u1ea5n an. C\u00f3 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c n\u1ed5i lo\u1ea1n trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng. C\u00f3 nh\u1eefng m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed1i ch\u1ea5t b\u1eb1ng m\u1ed3m mi\u1ec7ng hay th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u1ea3 ch\u00e2n tay, r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Argentina y\u00eau c\u1ea7u HLV tr\u1ea3 l\u1ea1i b\u1ed9 t\u1ee9 v\u1ec7 cho h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng, h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng n\u00f3i n\u0103ng g\u00ec nh\u01b0 v\u1eady. Javier Mascherano ngang nhi\u00ean t\u1ef1 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t r\u1ed3i l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng, anh kh\u00f4ng l\u00e0m v\u1eady. Nh\u01b0ng, \u0111\u1ed3n \u0111o\u00e1n cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng n\u00e0y c\u00f3 v\u1ebb \u0111\u00e1ng tin nh\u1ea5t, khi n\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3i th\u00edch \u1edf vi\u1ec7c l\u00e3o t\u01b0\u1edbng 34 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh \u1edf khu trung tuy\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Nigeria.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi \u0111\u01b0a Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1eeda t\u1eed Lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng ch\u00f3i h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" title=\"Messi \u0111\u01b0a Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1eeda t\u1eed Lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng ch\u00f3i h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 2\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Messi-dua-Argentina-vuot-qua-cua-tu-Luon-la-mot-ngoi-sao-sang-choi-hon-tat-ca!-hinh-anh-2.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Javier Mascherano ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c c\u1ee7a Argentina su\u00fdt ch\u00fat n\u1eefa tan t\u00e0nh m\u00e2y kh\u00f3i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ebf r\u1ed3i, Mascherano \u0111\u00e3 nh\u1eadp vai ph\u1ea3n di\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o h\u01a1n, k\u00e9o ng\u00e3 Leon Balogun trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u1edf t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00e1 ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c c\u1ee7a Oghenekaro Etebo. Qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c, m\u1ed9t pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1eb3ng v\u00e0 ng\u1edd ngh\u1ec7ch h\u01a1n m\u00e0 anh kh\u00f3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd t\u1eeb ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e2n c\u1ee7a n\u00f3, m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ea1n d\u00e0y kinh nghi\u1ec7m d\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng n\u0103m th\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec9nh cao c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh kho\u00e1c \u00e1o nh\u1eefng Liverpool r\u1ed3i Barcelona.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, gi\u1edbi m\u1ed9 \u0111i\u1ec7u \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd s\u1ebd c\u00f2n x\u01b0\u1edbng t\u00ean Mascherano d\u00e0i d\u00e0i nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t th\u1ee9 quy\u1ec1n l\u1ef1c \u0111en ch\u1ebft ch\u00f3c trong ph\u00f2ng thay \u0111\u1ed3 Argentina, tr\u1edb tr\u00eau thay n\u1ebfu danh x\u01b0ng t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c san s\u1ebb cho Marcos Rojo sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u1ee5ng v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ecba.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Kh\u00f4ng, trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Manchester United \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 &ldquo;r\u00f9a&rdquo;. Qu\u1ea3 penalty m\u01b0\u1eddi m\u01b0\u01a1i \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn m\u1eb7c cho tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i tai ti\u1ebfng Cuneyt Cakir \u0111\u00e3 tham kh\u1ea3o c\u1ea3 VAR v\u00ec l\u00fd do&hellip; v\u00f4 t\u00ecnh, kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khi quy\u1ec7n l\u1eabn trong s\u1ef1 ph\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ed1i d\u1eef d\u1ed9i c\u1ee7a ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nigeria.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Rojo tho\u00e1t vai t\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed3, anh th\u1eadm ch\u00ed s\u1eafm lu\u00f4n v\u1ecb th\u1ebf ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng v\u1edbi c\u00fa b\u0103ng c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ec7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0o g\u00f3c ch\u1ebft khung th\u00e0nh \u1edf nh\u1eefng ph\u00fat cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u01b0a Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1eeda t\u1eed \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi \u0111\u01b0a Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1eeda t\u1eed Lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng ch\u00f3i h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" title=\"Messi \u0111\u01b0a Argentina v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u1eeda t\u1eed Lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng ch\u00f3i h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3! h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh 3\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Messi-dua-Argentina-vuot-qua-cua-tu-Luon-la-mot-ngoi-sao-sang-choi-hon-tat-ca!-hinh-anh-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marcos Rojo s\u1eafm vai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng nh\u01b0ng Leo Messi \u1edf tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina v\u1eabn l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng nh\u1ea5t!</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t c\u00f4ng nho nh\u1ecf nh\u01b0ng c\u00f3 l\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u00ednh Rojo vui v\u1ebb ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ti\u00eau \u0111i\u1ec3m ch\u00f3i l\u1ecdi nh\u1ea5t v\u1eabn s\u1ebd lu\u00f4n thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Lionel Messi, li\u00ean t\u01b0\u1edfng ngay \u1edf h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u00f5ng tr\u00ean l\u01b0ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i si\u00eau sao khi \u0103n m\u1eebng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng gi\u1ea3i c\u1ee9u c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t d\u00e2n t\u1ed9c \u0111\u00f3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Messi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u1ee3i m\u1edf t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 cho tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh v\u00e0 ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf n\u00e0y, v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng khai th\u00f4ng th\u1ebf b\u1ebf t\u1eafc tuy\u1ec7t m\u1ef9 nh\u01b0 b\u1ea5t t\u1eadn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec ch\u00fang ta \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u00f4ng th\u1ea5y \u1edf \u0111\u00f4i ch\u00e2n thi\u00ean t\u00e0i n\u00e0y xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t c\u1ea3 th\u1eadp k\u1ef7 \u0111\u00e3 qua, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa nh\u1eadn ra m\u00ecnh th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 may m\u1eafn v\u00e0 di\u1ec5m ph\u00fac ra sao. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-argentina-vs-nigeria-463-189665.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/clip-ban-thang-argentina-vs-nigeria.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-argentina-vs-nigeria-463-189665.html\">Nigeria 1-2 Argentina (KT): C\u1ee9u tinh Rojo \u0111\u01b0a Albiceleste v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 c\u1ef1c ngo\u1ea1n m\u1ee5c</span><br>\r\nMessi v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng qua khe c\u1eeda h\u1eb9p sau 90 ph\u00fat ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf. Messi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0ng Moses g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m. Cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn, Argentina may m\u1eafn...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Sampaoli l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn l\u01b0\u1ee3c gia v\u1edbi t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 t\u00ean tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh, nh\u01b0ng World Cup 2018 sau c\u00f9ng v\u1eabn c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem nh\u01b0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Argentina l\u00e0 chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng cho Messi. \u0110\u1ea5u ph\u00e1p t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng duy nh\u1ea5t trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a Argentina l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng cho Messi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Anh ch\u1eb3ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nh\u01b0 Jose Mourinho hay Pep Guardiola \u0111\u1ec3 r\u00fat ra k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng m\u1ed9t s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u00fd t\u01b0\u1edfng nghe \u1ed5n nh\u1ea5t. Th\u1ea7y ch\u1ecbu th\u00ec tr\u00f2 l\u00e0m, Messi \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ef1 t\u00ecm ra s\u1ef1 c\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 cho m\u00ecnh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-nghet-tho-truoc-nigeria-421-189686.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/27/messi-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-nghet-tho-truoc-nigeria.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/messi-noi-gi-sau-chien-thang-nghet-tho-truoc-nigeria-421-189686.html\">Messi n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria?</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria t\u1ed1i 26/6, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Messi cho bi\u1ebft anh v\u00e0 c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o vi\u1ec7c Argentina s\u1ebd c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, s\u1ef1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc c\u1ee7a \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n v\u01b0\u1ee3t tuy\u1ebfn c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb xem th\u01b0\u1eddng. Ever Banega ch\u01b0a \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u1eadn n\u00e0o \u1edf World Cup 2018 cho \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina vs Nigeria, m\u1ed9t trong c\u1ea3 chu\u1ed7i c\u00e2u h\u1ecfi xoay quanh nh\u1eefng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 nh\u00e2n s\u1ef1 b\u1ea5t h\u1ee3p \u00fd c\u1ee7a Sampaoli.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Sevilla v\u00e0 Inter Milan tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t nh\u1ea1c tr\u01b0\u1edfng v\u1edbi s\u1ee9c s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o b\u1ea5t t\u1eadn, nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u1ed3ng th\u1eddi c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea3m \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00e1ch nhi\u1ec7m c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t \u00f4ng ch\u1ee7 c\u1ea7m tr\u1ecbch v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft th\u1ebf c\u1ee5c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Trong l\u00f2ng m\u1ed9t tuy\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa t\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ed1i v\u00f4 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0 k\u1ef7 lu\u1eadt, s\u1ef1 \u0111i\u1ec1m t\u0129nh v\u00e0 t\u1ec9nh t\u00e1o c\u1ee7a Banega l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 then ch\u1ed1t v\u00e0 th\u1eadt \u0111i\u00ean r\u1ed3 n\u1ebfu anh ph\u1ea3i tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong si\u00eau \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn kinh \u0111i\u1ec3n g\u1eb7p Ph\u00e1p.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi o tran Nigeria 1-2 Argentina\" title=\"Messi \u1edf tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/messi-dua-argentina-vuot-qua-cua-tu-luon-la-mot-ngoi-sao-sang-choi-hon-tat-ca.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leo Messi \u1edf tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 b\u1eb1ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p \u0111\u00fang ch\u1ea5t thi\u00ean t\u00e0i</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">C\u00f9ng tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi Messi v\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n nh\u01b0 v\u1ebb b\u1ec1 ngo\u00e0i c\u1ee7a n\u00f3, ch\u1eb3ng n\u00f3i ri\u00eang chuy\u1ec7n hi\u1ec7n h\u1eefu trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sinh t\u1eed c\u1ee7a Argentina. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i s\u1ed1ng ti\u1ebfp b\u00f3ng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i nh\u1eb9 nh\u00e0ng t\u1ef1a l\u00f4ng h\u1ed3ng, trong khi 99% s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p c\u1ee7a anh tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ebfn 2-3 nh\u1ecbp ch\u1ea1m m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 x\u1eed l\u00fd v\u00e0 ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng v\u1edbi b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n \u0111ang di chuy\u1ec3n ch\u1ea1y ch\u1ed7 v\u1edbi t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u01b0 v\u1eady.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Trong m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc ng\u1eafn ng\u1ee7i, Messi d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 qu\u1eb3ng g\u00e1nh \u00e2u lo, \u00e1p l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1eb7t l\u00ean \u0111\u00f4i vai \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 s\u1ed1ng tr\u1ecdn v\u1edbi b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1, \u0111\u1ec3 r\u1ed3i t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ai ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c trao tr\u1ecdn \u0111\u1ee9c tin v\u00e0 hy v\u1ecdng n\u01a1i anh m\u00e0 th\u00f4i. \u0110\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n m\u00e0 tuy\u1ec7t h\u1ea3o, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 v\u1ebb \u0111\u1eb9p c\u1ee7a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-argentina-vs-nigeria-421-189676.html\" target=\"_blank\">Argentina vs Nigeria</span>.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Messi\" title=\"Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/e.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Leo Messi \u1edf tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina: Lu\u00f4n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao s\u00e1ng ch\u00f3i h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3!</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u0169ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t c\u00e1ch phi th\u01b0\u1eddng, kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 b\u1edfi n\u00f3 xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t t\u1eeb c\u00e1i ch\u00e2n kh\u00f4ng thu\u1eadn c\u1ee7a Messi m\u00e0 l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 quy\u1ebft \u0111o\u00e1n \u1edf anh trong ho\u00e0n c\u1ea3nh n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1, ng\u1ed9t ng\u1ea1t s\u1ee9c \u00e9p \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi. N\u00f3 g\u1ee3i nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00fa s\u00fat c\u1ee7a Michael Owen tung l\u01b0\u1edbi ch\u00ednh Argentina \u1edf France 98, m\u1ed9t c\u00e1i g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n b\u1ea3n n\u0103ng \u1edf m\u1ed9t c\u1eadu nh\u00f3c tu\u1ed5i teen v\u1edbi ch\u1eb3ng c\u00f3 g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ea5t c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u1ea3 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">\u0110\u1eb1ng n\u00e0y, \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 hai th\u1eadp ni\u00ean sau \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb m\u1ed9t g\u00e3 trai 31 tu\u1ed5i g\u00e1nh v\u00e1c c\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u00ean \u0111\u00f4i vai v\u00e0 h\u1ee9ng ch\u1ecbu \u0111\u1ee7 th\u1ee9 h\u1ec9 n\u1ed9 \u00e1i \u1ed1 t\u1eeb th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, v\u1edbi ph\u1ea7n \u0111a \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng th\u1eddi ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u00e1nh nh\u00ecn soi m\u00f3i, x\u00e9t n\u00e9t v\u00e0 t\u00e2m l\u00fd s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i ng\u00e3 g\u1ee5c \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn. N\u1ebfu c\u00f2n b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 khi\u1ebfn anh ng\u1ea1c nhi\u00ean v\u1ec1 Messi, r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 anh ch\u01b0a xem b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 ham m\u00ea m\u00e0 th\u00f4i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-argentina-vs-nigeria-461-189678.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nigeria 1-2 Argentina (B\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">&ldquo;Ng\u00e0y mai Argentina s\u1ebd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u chi\u1ebfn d\u1ecbch World Cup c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.&rdquo; &ndash; Tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 nghe c\u00f3 v\u1ebb s\u00e1o r\u1ed7ng v\u00e0 s\u1ebfn s\u00faa nh\u01b0 phim c\u1ee7a Sampaoli trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Argentina vs Nigeria, \u00edt nhi\u1ec1u c\u00f2n th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n s\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng n\u01a1i ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e0n \u00f4ng nh\u1ecf th\u00f3 n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\">Th\u1ebf r\u1ed3i trong \u0111\u00eam St. Petersburg ch\u01b0a \u0111\u1ea7y 24h \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 sau, khi v\u1eadn m\u1ec7nh n\u01b0\u1edbc nh\u00e0 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00f4ng vi\u1ec7c v\u00e0 ti\u1ebfng t\u0103m c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh \u0111ang \u0111\u1ee9ng b\u00ean b\u1edd v\u1ef1c th\u1eb3m, nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u00e3 soi s\u00e1ng con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng sinh cho Sampaoli v\u00e0 Argentina. Nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t l\u1ebd th\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean ki\u1ec3u d\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ecbnh l\u00fd mu\u00f4n thu\u1edf, m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao lu\u00f4n ch\u00f3i l\u1ecdi h\u01a1n t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align:justify\"><strong>Gia Khoa (TTVN)</strong><o:p></o:p></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"610","checkdouble":"189690"},{"date":"06:40 27/06","title":"3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Nigeria 1-2 Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/6/27/3-nguoi-chien-thang-va-4-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-nigeria-12-argentina.png","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Argentina \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria 2-1 \u0111\u1ea7y k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua danh s\u00e1ch 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Leo Messi</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng Leo Messi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Iceland anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 11 l\u1ea7n, trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 1 l\u1ea7n tr\u00ean ch\u1ea5m 11m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. \u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m duy nh\u1ea5t 1 l\u1ea7n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Nigeria vs Argentina b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Nigeria vs Argentina b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/Du-am-Nigeria-vs-Argentina-bang-D-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Messi ghi b\u00e0n gi\u00fap Argentina v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Messi khi\u1ebfn Argentina ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland v\u00e0 Croatia, nh\u1eefng s\u1ef1 ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch nh\u1eafm v\u00e0o M10 khi\u1ebfn anh ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n nh\u1ea5t Messi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft b\u1ea3ng D v\u1edbi Nigeria, Messi \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1987 l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Argentina ngay \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 14. Ng\u00f4i sao 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i 662 ph\u00fat kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a M10 \u1edf World Cup.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u1ec9 c\u00f3 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp cho Argentina \u1edf 3 k\u1ef3 World Cup li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp. Diego Maradona (1982, 1986, 1994), Gabriel Batistuta (1994, 1998, 2002) v\u00e0 Lionel Messi (2006, 2014, 2018).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0ng quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t, b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Messi \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap Argentina \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria 2-1 qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 video VAR l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 mang \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 tranh c\u00e3i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn \u1edf World Cup 2018. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Argentina v\u00e0 Nigeria, m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y l\u1ea1i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cong nghe VAR lai gay tranh cai o tran Nigeria vs Argentina\" title=\"C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/var.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i \u1edf tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nMarcos Rojo \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh cho Nigeria \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng 11m, nh\u01b0ng sau khi xem l\u1ea1i c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh d\u00f9 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u00e1o xanh ph\u1ea3n \u1ee9ng gay g\u1eaft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nJon Obi Mikel n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Nigria vs Argentina, c\u1ef1u sao Chelsea kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp nh\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1ee3i t\u1eeb quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;\u0110\u00f3 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t qu\u1ea3 11m cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y b\u00f3ng ch\u1ea1m tay Rojo trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m. Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u00f4ng \u1ea5y c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i h\u01b0\u1edfng 11, sau \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng \u1ea5y xem l\u1ea1i video v\u00e0 thay \u0111\u1ed5i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&quot;Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i nh\u00ecn v\u00e0o VAR. \u00d4ng \u1ea5y n\u00f3i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea1m tay, t\u00f4i h\u1ecfi t\u1ea1i sao kh\u00f4ng cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng 11m, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y n\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u t\u1ea1i sao \u00f4ng \u1ea5y l\u1ea1i t\u1eeb ch\u1ed1i 1 qu\u1ea3 11m h\u1ee3p l\u1ec7 m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u01b0\u1edfng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTi\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Nordin Amrabat c\u1ee7a Ma R\u1ed1c kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea7n ng\u1ea1i d\u00f9ng nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi l\u1ebd n\u1eb7ng n\u1ec1 sau khi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh b\u1ecb VAR t\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc T\u00e2y Ban Nha.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Iran c\u0169ng t\u1ed1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i thi\u00ean v\u1ecb khi ph\u1edbt l\u1edd th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf cho Ronaldo d\u00f9 \u0111\u00e3 tham kh\u1ea3o VAR. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 m\u1edbi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng \u1edf World Cup 2018 \u0111ang \u0111em \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 tranh c\u00e3i r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Ever Banega</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, Messi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u l\u00e0 do kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tr\u1ee3 gi\u00fap c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft t\u1eeb c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nigeria, M10 \u0111\u00e3 nguy hi\u1ec3m h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ever Banega co mot tran dau an tuong\" title=\"Ever Banega c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/banega.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ever Banega c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nEver Banega ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n cung c\u1ea5p b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh \u0111\u1ec3 Messi ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c l\u00ean b\u00f3ng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m. Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Sevilla l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o \u0111\u1ec3 M10 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o gi\u00fap Messi ghi b\u00e0n, Banega c\u00f2n l\u00e0 trung t\u00e2m trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Argentina, anh l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi tung ra nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn Nigeria vs Argentina b\u1ea3ng D World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1988 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Argentina c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria qua \u0111\u00f3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu Argentina mu\u1ed1n l\u00e0m n\u00ean b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, Ever Banega ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, HLV Sampaoli ch\u1ec9 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 36 ph\u00fat trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Iceland v\u00e0 Croatia.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Javier Mascherano</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">4 n\u0103m tr\u01b0\u1edbc, t\u1ea1i World Cup 2014, Javier Mascherano l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hay nh\u1ea5t \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Brazil. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a c\u1ef1u sao Liverpool \u0111\u00e3 sa s\u00fat r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Javier Mascherano choi te hai truoc Nigeria\" title=\"Javier Mascherano ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/mas.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Javier Mascherano ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nQu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Barca bu\u1ed9c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 34 tu\u1ed5i ph\u1ea3i ra \u0111i, anh \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn Trung Qu\u1ed1c thay v\u00ec m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng kh\u00e1c \u1edf ch\u00e2u \u00c2u. \u1ede m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 t\u00ednh c\u1ea1nh tranh qu\u00e1 cao, d\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u01b0 Javier Mascherano ng\u00e0y c\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh m\u1ea5t m\u00ecnh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1984 \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nigeria, anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u00f9ng t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng. Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u00e1nh ch\u1eb7n, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 34 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f2n th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9, ch\u1ecdn v\u1ecb tr\u00ed k\u00e9m, kh\u00f4ng nhanh nh\u1eady trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng v\u00e0o b\u00f3ng, Mascherano \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Argentina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nN\u1ebfu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 34 tu\u1ed5i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ch\u01a1i nh\u01b0 v\u1eady \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p thu\u1ed9c v\u00f2ng 1/8, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t mong manh.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng: Marcos Rojo</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o cho MU ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Argentina \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nigeria. Ph\u00fat 86, t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u0103ng ngang bi\u00ean v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a Gabriel Mercado, Rojo ch\u1ea1y c\u1eaft m\u1eb7t v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u00e0o g\u00f3c xa \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Uzoho.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Marcos Rojo Leo Messi\" title=\"Marcos Rojo Leo Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/diem-nhan-du-am-nigeria-vs-argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Marcos Rojo tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng c\u1ee7a Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u00ednh pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 gi\u00fap Argentina \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nigeria 2-1 qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nMarcos Rojo \u0111\u00e3 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG, 2 trong 3 b\u00e0n \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Nigeria (\u1edf World Cup 2014 anh c\u0169ng ghi b\u00e0n v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi &ldquo;\u0110\u1ea1i b\u00e0ng xanh&rdquo;).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y d\u00f9 kh\u00f4ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean ra s\u00e2n trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o M.U \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, nh\u01b0ng trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG anh v\u1eabn l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Argentina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Odion Ighalo</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kelechi Iheanacho ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p 2 HLV Gernot Rohr \u0111\u00e3 r\u00fat ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Leicester v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0a v\u00e0o s\u00e2n Odion Ighalo.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Odion Ighalo choi that vong o World Cup 2018\" title=\"Odion Ighalo ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf World Cup 2018\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/ighano.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Odion Ighalo ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng \u1edf World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00d4ng th\u1ea7y 64 tu\u1ed5i mu\u1ed1n t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u00e0n l\u01b0\u1edbt c\u1ee7a Ighalo \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1edbi h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Argentina. Tuy nhi\u00ean, Ighalo kh\u00f4ng th\u1ebb th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n \u00fd \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt m\u00e0 HLV Gernot Rohr mong mu\u1ed1n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n45 ph\u00fat c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Ighalo ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 19 l\u1ea7n v\u00e0 tung ra 1 pha d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch. 3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 29 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i: Willy Caballero</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Willy Caballero \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iceland v\u00e0 Croatia. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Iceland anh li\u00ean t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i v\u1ecb tr\u00ed, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 36 tu\u1ed5i c\u0169ng t\u1ecf ra ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p trong nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng ph\u1ea3n x\u1ea1.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Willy Caballero ngoi du bi o tran gap Nigeria\" title=\"Willy Caballero ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nigeria\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/27/cableero.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Willy Caballero ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nigeria</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Croatia anh m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng \u1edf b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00e0. Theo \u0111\u00f3, anh chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ec3 Ante Rebic m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi nh\u1eefng sai l\u1ea7m nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb trong tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-argentina-vs-nigeria-463-189665.html\" target=\"_blank\">Nigeria vs Argentina</span>.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFranco Armani \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn b\u1eaft ch\u00ednh, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i kh\u00e1 t\u1ed1t. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Franco Armani \u0111\u00e1p \u1ee9ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 tin t\u01b0\u1edfng, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Willy Caballero s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi c\u1ee7a \u0110T Argentina.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"609","checkdouble":"189693"},{"date":"15:49 26/06","title":"\"Sterling ph\u1ea3i nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1ecb tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh cho Rashford \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p B\u1ec9\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/sterling.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sam Allardyce ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Raheem Sterling, c\u1ef1u HLV tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Gareth Southgate c\u1ea7n lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u1ec3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Raheem Sterling.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Raheem Sterling g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Raheem Sterling \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1994 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gareth Southgate b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o v\u1edbi Harry Kane trong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sam Allardyce ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Raheem Sterling h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sam Allardyce ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Raheem Sterling h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/21/Sam-Allardyce-phat-bieu-ve-Raheem-Sterling-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Sterling \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Southgate trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nN\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Harry Kane ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u00ec Sterling l\u1ea1i g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Panama, Sterling c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 24 tu\u1ed5i b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Kh\u00f4ng \u00edt \u00fd ki\u1ebfn cho r\u1eb1ng HLV Gareth Southgate n\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Man City ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, trong m\u1ed9t bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp HLV Southgate \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt, theo \u0111\u00f3 <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ro-ri-doi-hinh-anh-gap-panama-sterling-lam-nguy-421-189246.html\" target=\"_blank\">Sterling ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Panama</span>, nh\u01b0ng r\u1ed3i anh v\u1eabn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sam Allardyce mu\u1ed1n Rashford thay th\u1ebf Sterling</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sam Allardyce ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Raheem Sterling, c\u1ef1u HLV tuy\u1ec3n Anh kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh HLV Gareth Southgate c\u1ea7n lo\u1ea1i b\u1ecf ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Man City \u0111\u1ec3 trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Rashford.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Big Sam cho rang Sterling phai ngoi du bi cho Rashford\" title=\"Big Sam cho r\u1eb1ng Sterling ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Rashford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/sterling.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Big Sam cho r\u1eb1ng Sterling ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb cho Rashford</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 l\u00fd do n\u00e0o \u0111\u1ec3 Gareth Southgate ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tin t\u01b0\u1edfng Sterling, 2 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 qu\u00e1 \u0111\u1ee7 r\u1ed3i. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u01b0 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Man City, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng ng\u1ed3i d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Rashford \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t trong nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu tr\u01b0\u1edbc World Cup 2018, \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn l\u00fac c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng ngay t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n Gareth Southgate trao c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i cho Rashford, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ec9&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"608","checkdouble":"189625"},{"date":"16:02 26/06","title":"Wenger ch\u1ec9 ra m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/19/wenger-chi-ra-mat-xich-yeu-kem-nhat-cua-dt-anh.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, c\u1ef1u HLV Arsenal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Kyle Walker l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kyle Walker kh\u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, Kyle Walker l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ea1t phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Man City. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1990 \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Gareth Southgate b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 \u1edf World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/13/Arsene-Wenger-phat-bieu-ve-DT-Anh-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kyle Walker ch\u01a1i thi\u1ebfu \u1ed5n \u0111\u1ecbnh trong hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 3-5-2, Walker \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Harry Maguire v\u00e0 John Stones \u1edf h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi. Trong s\u1ed1 3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Gareth Southgate tin t\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 28 tu\u1ed5i l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Tunisia ch\u00ednh <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/kyle-walker-cau-thu-thuy-si-tu-lao-vao-cui-cho-cua-toi-469-188898.html\" target=\"_blank\">Walker l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i khi\u1ebfn Anh ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 1 qu\u1ea3 11m</span>, \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Panama c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y c\u0169ng th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean b\u1ecf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n thi\u1ebfu \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1990 khi\u1ebfn NHM S\u01b0 t\u1eed Anh r\u1ea5t lo l\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nS\u1edf tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a Walker l\u00e0 ch\u1ea1y c\u00e1nh ph\u1ea3i trong h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ed1 tr\u00ed \u0111\u00e1 trong h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c cho th\u1ea5y nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Wenger kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao Walker</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsene Wenger ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 \u0110T Anh, c\u1ef1u HLV Arsenal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Kyle Walker l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Tam s\u01b0 \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kyle Walker\" title=\"Kyle Walker\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/19/wenger-chi-ra-mat-xich-yeu-kem-nhat-cua-dt-anh.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wenger \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 kh\u00f4ng cao Kyle Walker trong h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;C\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i trong m\u1ed9t h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p trong vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t trung v\u1ec7. Southgate n\u00ean t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi qu\u00e1 mu\u1ed9n. Anh v\u1eabn c\u00f2n Eric Dier, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u00e1 trung v\u1ec7 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, Dier h\u1ee3p h\u01a1n l\u00e0 Walker trong h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Anh \u1edf 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao, nh\u01b0ng Walker \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ed9c l\u1ed9 nh\u1eefng v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1. Khi g\u1eb7p nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng l\u1edbn c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i h\u01a1n n\u1eefa, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng Southgate c\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 thay \u0111\u1ed5i c\u00e0ng nhanh c\u00e0ng t\u1ed1t&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n&ldquo;Walker \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1eaft x\u00edch y\u1ebfu nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Anh, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd n\u1ebfu c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c m\u1eafc sai l\u1ea7m khi bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 \u1edf h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng g\u1ed3m 3&nbsp;h\u1eadu v\u1ec7&rdquo;.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<br></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"607","checkdouble":"189626"},{"date":"16:11 26/06","title":"5 s\u01a1 \u0111\u1ed3 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt gi\u00fap Argentina h\u1ea1 Nigeria \u0111\u1ec3 m\u01a1 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/26/5-so-do-chien-thuat-giup-argentina-ha-nigeria-de-mo-ve-di-tiep.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Theo Mirror, HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Arsene Wenger t\u1eebng quan t\u00e2m Lewis Dunk</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u1eeba qua, trung v\u1ec7 Lewis Dunk l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ch\u01a1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh c\u1ee7a Brighton.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/arsenal-nham-sao-brighton-nang-cap-hang-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Wenger t\u1eebng mu\u1ed1n Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNg\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1991 ra s\u00e2n trong c\u1ea3 38 tr\u1eadn \u1edf Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Brighton tr\u1ee5 h\u1ea1ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLewis Dunk c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ch\u1ed1ng b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng t\u1ed1t, anh c\u0169ng li\u00ean k\u1ebft c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u1edbi c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i. HLV Arsene Wenger \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 27 tu\u1ed5i, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n BL\u0110 Arsenal \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong danh s\u00e1ch nh\u1eefng t\u00e2n binh m\u00e0 Arsenal mu\u1ed1n mua \u1edf H\u00e8 2018, Lewis Dunk l\u00e0 m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u. \u201cGi\u00e1o s\u01b0\u201d nh\u1eafm c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1991 nh\u01b0 s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf l\u00e2u d\u00e0i cho Laurent Koscielny.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chi 22 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng mua ng\u00f4i sao ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh, h\u1ecd hy v\u1ecdng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00f4i k\u00e9o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh t\u1edbi s\u00e2n Emrates.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Arsenal t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Lewis Dunk</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng Arsenal mua Lewis Dunk th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf H\u00e8 2018 l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao. Theo Mirror, HLV Unai Emery kh\u00f4ng h\u1ee9ng th\u00fa v\u1edbi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 chuy\u1ec3n sang nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau kh\u00e1c.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lewis Dunk\" title=\"Lewis Dunk\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/5/7/dunk.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Arsenal t\u1eeb b\u1ecf Lewis Dunk v\u00ec Emery kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ef1u HLV PSG kh\u00f4ng th\u00edch phong c\u00e1ch thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Lewis Dunk, \u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Sokratis c\u1ee7a Dortmund h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Brighton. Theo nhi\u1ec1u ngu\u1ed3n tin, Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eedi l\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1 ngh\u1ecb tr\u1ecb gi\u00e1 17 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng h\u1ecfi mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Hy L\u1ea1p.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/arsenal-tra-gia-dat-koscielny-chan-thuong-nang-mat-world-cup-184-185546.html\" target=\"_blank\">Laurent Koscielny d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng</span> v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 12 m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i, b\u1edfi v\u1eady HLV Emery bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p trung v\u1ec7 v\u1edbi Mustafi.\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nArsenal v\u1eabn c\u00f2n \u0111\u00f3 Chambers hay Holding, song nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 trong th\u1eddi gian g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o h\u1ecd l\u00e0 s\u1ef1 m\u1ea1o hi\u1ec3m r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"606","checkdouble":"189628"},{"date":"16:03 26/06","title":"Nh\u1